ll I remember the first, well I - I don't remember but - I was on holiday at - in the country at my grandmother's, my sister told me, she got all - most of the things out of pawn that she had in. But they must have had something - to pawn them mustn't the
y. And then I think she got in with - like a bad lot at that time, drink. She started, she - she drank. Mm. But we were left - more or less to bring ourselves up, one - looking after the other. Mm.
